<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Fragments, apparently, of one <rs type="material" key="marmor">marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs>, with moulding above and a simple <rs type="decoration" reg="egg and dart moulding">egg and dart</rs> pattern on at least 3 sides; similar to <xref type="iAph">1203</xref> (=84.71). a: Upper left corner with moulding and egg and dart surviving above (<measure dim="none">0.57</measure>   × <measure dim="none">0.32</measure> x depth not known); b: Upper right corner with egg and dart surviving (<measure dim="none">0.39</measure>   × <measure dim="none">0.23</measure>   × <measure dim="none">0.32</measure>). </p>
</div>
